ity at a time alexis sales team leader my boss saw how much happier i was and how much more fulfilled i was every day he really encouraged me to pursue personal passions benefits our people are our greatest and most important resource thats why we support the personal and professional health and development of our employees – by providing each with insurance retirement benefits educational assistance and paid time off specific benefits vary by company open roles locations home how we work faq equal employment opportunity equal employment opportunity supplement family and medical leave act employee polygraph protection act any applicant who because of disability needs accommodation or assistance in completing this application or at any time during the application process may request assistance by clicking here koch companies do not solicit potential candidates by text message and do not request financial or banking information at any time during the interview process scroll